  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a nutrition intervention during a
      rehabilitation stay followed by nutritional advice after discharge, can improve the
      nutritional status of the patients after 3 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
